 <italic>i</italic> ≤ 
 <italic>r</italic>,1 ≤ 
 <italic>j</italic> ≤ 
 <italic>c</italic>} defines the cellular space, or a collection of 
 <italic>r</italic>×
 <italic>c</italic> cells on a two‐way array, where 
 <italic>r</italic>×
